{"word":"ἐνάλλομαι","slug":"ἐνάλλομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐνάλλομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ᾰλοῦμαι</el>) (aor1 <el>-ηλάμην</el>) (aor2 <el>-ηλόμην</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to leap in</i> or <i>upon</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to rush against</i> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to dance</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}